        Instantiates a new link specification.
        Parameters:
        id - the id
        categoryIds - the category IDs
        order - the sort order
        href - the linked resource (href)
        blank - specified whether to open the link in a blank target (default is false)
        text - the text that is displayed instead of the link
        textTranslations - the text translations
        description - the description
        descriptionTranslations - the description translations
